            <title>[WICKET-6161] SecuritySettings.setEnforceMounts() should be applicable for all kind of pages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6161</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently SecuritySettings.setEnforceMounts(true) works only for pages which do have mount point and doesn&apos;t work other bookmarkable pages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Issue discussed here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://markmail.org/message/ctoac6eq26kt5jve&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://markmail.org/message/ctoac6eq26kt5jve&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The point is to disallow of using /wicket/bookmarkable/ for all pages if enforceMounts was set to true.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
